- --------------
- --- Update ---
- --------------

SGI has released Patch 10033: SGI ProPack v2.3 security update, which
includes updated RPMs for SGI ProPack v2.3 for the Altix family of systems,
in response to the following erratas released by Red Hat:

 Updated stunnel packages available
 https://rhn.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2003-297.html

 Updated glibc packages fix various issues
 https://rhn.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2003-249.html


Patch 10033 is available from http://support.sgi.com/
or the individual RPMs from Patch 10033 are available from:
ftp://oss.sgi.com/projects/sgi_propack/download/2.3/updates/RPMS
ftp://oss.sgi.com/projects/sgi_propack/download/2.3/updates/SRPMS


